Dependencies
------------

* `webrtc-audio-processing <https://github.com/xiph/speexdsp>`_

Install
-------

.. code:: bash

    pip install webrtc_audio_processing

or
--

.. code:: bash

    git clone https://github.com/xiongyihui/webrtc-audio-processing-python.git
    cd webrtc-audio-processing-python
    python setup.py install

Import
------

.. code:: python

from webrtc_audio_processing import AudioProcessingModule
